commit 9250677cebcd94f5a4d89740703b7eae5722af03
Author: Nikhilesh S (nikki) <s.nikhilesh@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Jul 8 23:52:44 2009 +0300

    'Switch' GameObject added
    -------------------------
    - Added a generic 'Switch' GameObject that has a 'p_enabled' Python
      property and broadcasts 'on' and 'off' Python events, allowing good
      scriptability. So, it can be used for everything from disabling
      a MovingPlatform righ to going to the next level through changing
      dimension. Also has a 'built-in' SlidingBrush informer feature to allow
      Switches to easily control SlidingBrushes, which is what they'll mostly
      be used for, probably.

