    Dimension-Test, Lights
    ----------------------
    - Added a few walls in different dimensions to test. It works. And it's
      fun. :-)
    
    - Added a 'Light' GameObject type to be able to edit lighting in Blender
      with the same interface as the other objects. It works, but the actual
      lighting itself is a bit faulty because the test level geometry mesh
      was bad. Will be fixed.

